title: the most important types
pid: 38dd7b56-8089-491f-8de7-0951312fffa0
body: |2-
  - functions
    - map | dictionary
  - lists
  - sets
  - trees
  - (associative) maps | dictionaries
  - tables

  Your journey from data to statistical inference
  will usually end in a table, but
  the right way to get there
  might require some of the others.
